{"tid":204800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵死）復活節生意唔掂！旺角小食店：人就多，冇人買嘢食！","createTime":"2017-04-17T10:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T02:51:31.000Z","uid":29314,"like":115,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8c8a2914fba0029368b9a6d8fe16cb7f00cc9c3","tid":204800,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"花園街小食店店員符女士說，<span style=\"color: red;\">內地旅客一向佔整體生意約8成，惟復活節假期生意額不升反跌，其中內地客下跌一半</span>，「本地客都少咗出嚟，依家生意差好遠，平日生意都差」，以前每日可賣逾百斤魚蛋，現時平日僅30至40斤，假日亦只賣到60至70斤。"},{"pid":"8d83b167cfd9b15f8903fcc74a81dbed7f640fa3","tid":204800,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"Case 2:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於登打士街售賣豆花和腸粉的Annie說，復活節假期生意較平日上升約三分之一，但不算理想，「應該要再多少少，可能有啲人去咗旅行」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">她說復活節旅客沒有預期般多</span>，「過年都ok架，但今次真係少咗，可能市道差咗」，期望生意在暑假回升。她又說，沒有在假期加價或延長營業，「10蚊杯豆漿都唔係貴啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵死！！！"},{"pid":"d9ead9b202bf4a56e37dd28be6e17f8055733b9e","tid":204800,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"Case 3:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在西洋菜街售賣冷麵的店員指，復活節假期「唔似假期」，生意額很差，和平日差不多，「人就多，冇人買嘢食」，認為是經濟差，市民消費力下跌，及<span style=\"color: red;\">內地客減少所致</span>。"},{"pid":"ecfbf0ff22d0e16c6abf808d262d5fb2eb3eacd8","tid":204800,"uid":36251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"已經好耐無係旺角買呢啲野食<br />\n又貴又搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c780ad3fc2939071003c62b3fc5187797d6331f7","tid":204800,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸邊有復活假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbb62e8bef717a056f9fa5d38d3a40824d4d5f8","tid":204800,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"Case 4:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n位於鄰街的日式餐廳店長王女士則指，復活節假期一片死寂，原本預期假期生意額可與一般假日相若，但<span style=\"color: red;\">實際生意額卻下跌三分之二，街上人流亦大減</span>，是出乎意料的差，「可能啲人去晒旅行」。"},{"pid":"db28860dce732dfa4000b6c527c457cfbc41ddec","tid":204800,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c850a37b5ae85be4913b54833ffca023f371225d","tid":204800,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"條街真係少左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5ee98d287075f33bd5ea46eb4fa9a2ec96f53f","tid":204800,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"死開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5b83c2872afd4cee1d9ead0fdd14a9d1c488d7","tid":204800,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"model answer:<br />\n1. 佔中<br />\n2. 反水貨客示威<br />\n3. 旺角暴動"},{"pid":"30decf859b603aeb23a65ee3d583b3255ebe962d","tid":204800,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:46:34.000Z","msg":"靠大陸喱做生意啊嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d7f9bb6376c3182288df7b28dd0587b7d8f260","tid":204800,"uid":28184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"你地班鍵盤戰士攪到人地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b314981ad23b5a1fd5f28cc94ec8a63df0cf1afd","tid":204800,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"你都有今日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3853cab0df81b26d45c82de31b08a7ea9d64c464","tid":204800,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci