4800,"uid":17684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"陣味又臭、又貴、買野食重好似同d亞姐乞咁。你食埋我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a882919463f85122fc9aee9f92c7d10de63dd8d","tid":204800,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你地班無良小食店真係幫唔落手<br />\n一串魚蛋得個6粒夠膽死收我10蚊<br />\nD咖哩又唔入味是但淋上去就算<br />\n有D仲衰連個價錢都唔寫出黎<br />\n吉左比你先話你知一串20蚊局你比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n執左去就岩喇</blockquote><br />\n無價錢嗰啲點解會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問價已經篤緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後拎比您再答幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cd2e9e6001c978decdaf2177a1beb46f1639e1","tid":204800,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸邊有復活假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9你唔係咁都睇唔明啊？<br />\n佢既意思好明顯、以前復活節有大陸客所以生意都算好。<br />\nbtw少大陸客我行波鞋街都舒服好多。"},{"pid":"ac30d74e313e0d31ead6566a78dbf633cd727a53","tid":204800,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚都倚賴支那， 抵你地有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母、人地支那13億人口啊。靠香港人？個個都食到厭啦。"},{"pid":"ad857efc66c2258778391ff67e2698358a5657c8","tid":204800,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前唔係好好賺咩<br />\n<br />\n賺左個D咩黎?<br />\n<br />\n做生意都唔係100%賺啦<br />\n<br />\n大陸人多, 香港人唔黎買野<br />\n<br />\n你賣D野無咩特別, 同大陸無分別, 咁D大陸人做咩要落黎玩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n強國實行物嘢貨物打稅。<br />\n即係你係香港買多少少貨返大陸、跟住就打稅。<br />\n而且關口管水貨客好嚴。<br />\n所以宜家比以前好好多。<br />\n呢個亦都係我地想要的結果。"},{"pid":"549f4577a53c6987d8ad27af3194f140cceb8aae","tid":204800,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>10蚊杯豆漿都話唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n$10 去泰國食好多野啦 !</blockquote><br />\n你做乜唔話去強國可以買20杯啦。"},{"pid":"cff4f2d4e4ee04b2efb1b57c6c53bfbf507f7bbf","tid":204800,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你啦幾十蚊碗魚蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真呀,仲要唔好食<br />\n賣垃圾賣咁撚貴,拎比我隻狗食都唔撚得啦</blockquote><br />\n登打士街28蚊一份魚蛋撈麵。我屌佢老母"},{"pid":"92e9bcd98fb095409c45c09b44491207fe3fe741","tid":204800,"uid":26399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"仆街啦 一細碗牛雜50蚊啊"},{"pid":"33126eebd7c7a05861b2e8e108bd9bb164244dcc","tid":204800,"uid":5591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:47:09.000Z","msg":"蘿蔔沒揀過，筋太多，失敗！<br />\n豬皮煮得太爛，沒咬口，失敗！<br />\n豬血又鬆泡泡呀，一夾就散，失敗中的失敗！<br />\n最慘的就是大腸了，裏面根本沒洗乾淨，還有一舊屎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屎呀喂！</span></span>"},{"pid":"fdb280c7509fcfff472b7c181e550c8ff3747cb7","tid":204800,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窮撚邊敢消費 大劉講得岩 鬧撚醒晒 為左買樓連魚蛋唔敢篤呀 老闆你去叫誠哥食多2串拉</blockquote><br />\n有上進心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左買樓唔消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係 即使唔買樓 年紀大左都要比醫療費<br />\n<br />\n趁後生儲下錢好過啦<br />\n<br />\n消費? 不了"},{"pid":"89eada5b0b10d7c26e728832126e783ff79140d0","tid":204800,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"而家街邊小食仲貴過正餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9baf862ca79b497df98b4964242d97f4d5c98a3a","tid":204800,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"566bb0b6953d6d6b9a1a3040c8598cec8b2922f7","tid":204800,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:57:40.000Z","msg":"冇價錢果d擺明唔做你港燦生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲走去比錢食咁on9都講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013b3fb29021f633e00427308024f6e2b5804efe","tid":204800,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:01:51.000Z","msg":"因為大多數本地人唔會咁on9上當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aaa55c31a5da355b16bd74a4f683b4c337dbfbe","tid":204800,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Case 4:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n位於鄰街的日式餐廳店長王女士則指，復活節假期一片死寂，原本預期假期生意額可與一般假日相若，但<span style=\"color: red;\">實際生意額卻下跌三分之二，街上人流亦大減</span>，是出乎意料的差，「可能啲人去晒旅行」。</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家港人心態係喺香港盡量慳 留返啲錢嚟旅行"},{"pid":"4be177f283ad8f2150cacebdbe346cdd84ebf171","tid":204800,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千其唔好幫襯街邊小食......<br />\n<br />\n只會得到兩個結果、幫人交陀地費，幫人交租</blockquote><br />\n你真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ca9a1f37dcbf1c8b1fc0842773dc6da7d9ff96","tid":204800,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb73a8c6de5675058c3cdb64ac7bc851a3932a11","tid":204800,"uid":14182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家街邊小食仲貴過正餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪就係..十蚊得果五粒燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一包魷魚酥都收廿幾蚊，<br />\n我不如俾多少少食米線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e34c43d78bc26fe8ff81afc8a616d9a863e803","tid":204800,"uid":32015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"依啲鋪都唔撚係賣比我地食既"},{"pid":"5a1b1a8e2181239465447ddece3191d8fe4fdc94","tid":204800,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸邊有復活假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弱智都開舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d88f07d27b1f2b2646db4f61a13f68912f0c378","tid":204800,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Case 4:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n位於鄰街的日式餐廳店長王女士則指，復活節假期一片死寂，原本預期假期生意額可與一般假日相若，但<span style=\"color: red;\">實際生意額卻下跌三分之二，街上人流亦大減</span>，是出乎意料的差，「可能啲人去晒旅行」。</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家港人心態係喺香港盡量慳 留返啲錢嚟旅行</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錯樣樣都貴 質素又衰哂 平時lunch唔理 放假仲食你"},{"pid":"a8f6571c0247aa837faef0b16adf5f92848aee5d","tid":204800,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條街真係少左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個去哂旅行<br />\n<br />\n平時星期六日多人既商場都無乜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ab0c3746d211c8a32b7213b9f983e422bdf04a","tid":204800,"uid":93937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"唔信，第二個post話不留港消費唔會起到作用"},{"pid":"9f3a0a4fe41e07e96b7428bf33a841b8b1687e4d","tid":204800,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚都倚賴支那， 抵你地有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母、人地支那13億人口啊。靠香港人？個個都食到厭啦。</blockquote><br />\n97前又唔見大家樂封粒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89799936ba49f67e902e5076be18f2faf6e321ae","tid":204800,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Case 4:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n位於鄰街的日式餐廳店長王女士則指，復活節假期一片死寂，原本預期假期生意額可與一般假日相若，但<span style=\"color: red;\">實際生意額卻下跌三分之二，街上人流亦大減</span>，是出乎意料的差，「可能啲人去晒旅行」。</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家港人心態係喺香港盡量慳 留返啲錢嚟旅行</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錯樣樣都貴 質素又衰哂 平時lunch唔理 放假仲食你</blockquote><br />\n學樓上講 畀多少少錢食粉麵米線唔好？<br />\n而且而家慳得就慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不論為供樓定旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3ed45f1aa5e2dcb2023b37fdd89842ceb651c0","tid":204800,"uid":12036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"旺角最多香港人幫襯既應該係龍津?"},{"pid":"e68bd97398c5a48a897623a8b29494d98de5d287","tid":204800,"uid":12036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"旺角最多香港人幫襯既應該係龍津?"},{"pid":"9fa3789f90eb63d810f4b64daac702e1dd47aaa6","tid":204800,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"以前讀書都會幫襯下食下 個陣價錢都叫錢道 10蚊杯珍珠奶茶 7蚊串魚蛋10蚊4包撈麵 等等 而家不了 行街一定唔會出旺角 多人過佔中 同埋起個邊返過工 知道好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58607dd84ca208b112c9a4b024b2549f21efef6d","tid":204800,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"咪又係fatfat  <br />\n搵少左講到蝕咁"},{"pid":"e9fcda36f41f92df615e1caedd2f834db212e200","tid":204800,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你啦幾十蚊碗魚蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真呀,仲要唔好食<br />\n賣垃圾賣咁撚貴,拎比我隻狗食都唔撚得啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去啲傳統潮州魚旦粉舖頭 食碗真魚肉打成嘅淨旦 都唔洗咁貴 重好食好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc74b337c028bd5b50c58d33a707dc3bb414a61","tid":204800,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"10蚊豆漿唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我樓下6蚊，岩岩先加一蚊，<br />\n<br />\n無錯地區問題，咁你咪賣10蚊，<br />\n<br />\n我買我既6蚊"},{"pid":"dfdf71c20ab35a5035df35be1bfab59d464f89b1","tid":204800,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"要儲錢買樓，所以不了<br />\n<br />\n唔係既話班店主又會話班後生唔識儲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254c4f5ff33d0dabd3131485c0f3a7fb1ffdb7bd","tid":204800,"uid":68850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你地班無良小食店真係幫唔落手<br />\n一串魚蛋得個6粒夠膽死收我10蚊<br />\nD咖哩又唔入味是但淋上去就算<br />\n有D仲衰連個價錢都唔寫出黎<br />\n吉左比你先話你知一串20蚊局你比 <img src=\